{"tid":2191562,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國波特蘭續有反警暴與反種族歧視示威　有人擲炸彈 高呼Donald Trump FUCK OFF!!","createTime":"2020-09-06T13:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T14:44:30.000Z","uid":360777,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6ed69fce042bf152f724fa04428ba12ce30a0cda","tid":2191562,"uid":360777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:53:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548183-20200906.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548183-20200906.htm&d=uo2GI0poDlFkSsUZ5iwE4irXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=791fe1a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548183-20200906.htm&h=3abc2325\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548183-20200906.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國俄勒岡州波特蘭市的反種族主義及反警暴示威踏入第100日，有示威者向警員擲石頭及炸彈，警方施放催淚彈驅散，最少一人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n當地傳媒報道，大約400人當地星期六參與示威，從網上片段所見，有人向警員方向擲炸彈，一名示威者的腿部著火，警方批評示威者作出暴力行為，已經採取拘捕行動，但無透露有幾多人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n自從黑人弗洛伊德今年5月懷疑被警員暴力執法致死後，全國多處都有反種族歧視及反警暴示威，總統特朗普日前簽署備忘錄，威脅削減對波特蘭等失去法治城市的資助。"},{"pid":"f6687ecd10902dbc69394d117b105cf876a81973","tid":2191562,"uid":29528,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6ed69fce042bf152f724fa04428ba12ce30a0cda","tid":2191562,"uid":360777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:53:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548183-20200906.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548183-20200906.htm&d=uo2GI0poDlFkSsUZ5iwE4irXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=791fe1a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548183-20200906.htm&h=3abc2325\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548183-20200906.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國俄勒岡州波特蘭市的反種族主義及反警暴示威踏入第100日，有示威者向警員擲石頭及炸彈，警方施放催淚彈驅散，最少一人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n當地傳媒報道，大約400人當地星期六參與示威，從網上片段所見，有人向警員方向擲炸彈，一名示威者的腿部著火，警方批評示威者作出暴力行為，已經採取拘捕行動，但無透露有幾多人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n自從黑人弗洛伊德今年5月懷疑被警員暴力執法致死後，全國多處都有反種族歧視及反警暴示威，總統特朗普日前簽署備忘錄，威脅削減對波特蘭等失去法治城市的資助。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:57:23.000Z","msg":"篇文邊撚到有寫示威者高呼Donald Trump fuck off<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df29cfce8e0c8db65727e8d02df242bc11318a1","tid":2191562,"uid":346260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T14:16:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該借個位嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[實用文] 教您點先可以保障私隱、網絡安全<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2185179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2185179</a><br />\n<br />\n樓主可唔可以置頂？唔該曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0850f6c4277df24ec9efb7df501cc43152e070af","tid":2191562,"uid":360777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6df29cfce8e0c8db65727e8d02df242bc11318a1","tid":2191562,"uid":346260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T14:16:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該借個位嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[實用文] 教您點先可以保障私隱、網絡安全<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2185179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2185179</a><br />\n<br />\n樓主可唔可以置頂？唔該曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T14:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\